    <item>
      <title>汽车制造商担心关税 车价或上涨 3,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税将威胁到北美各地汽车制造商的生产，并导致汽车价格创下新高，约 2500 亿美元的贸易将受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
